    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Demo for Anarchy Hops will include just a boss fight, and will later be updated to include parts of the first chapter of the game.</strong><br><br>Hop and slash your way through multiple different factions to get back what was taken from you! Explore the internet,try on different outfits, and engage in some hyper violence as our protagonist Anarchy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Browse the internet and read through forums,read through BunnySpace profiles and don't get gnomed! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chat with friends and enemies alike on HiChat!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master a high speed, high lethality combat system </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun playing various minigames around the world! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know a large cast of unique,interesting characters all with stylized art and animations to personalize them </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retry missions freely and complete challenges to unlock new outfits and weapons! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294470/extras/089d0cfd7aebc89fd3bc3d559bac3256.poster.avif?t=1729047955\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294470/extras/089d0cfd7aebc89fd3bc3d559bac3256.webm?t=1729047955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294470/extras/089d0cfd7aebc89fd3bc3d559bac3256.mp4?t=1729047955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
